  "title": "Wrong filter for multiple facet.",
  "body": "Hello,\r\nI have a case that I can't understand, for the example: https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/examples/e-commerce/\r\n\r\nIn Material filter, I select Polypropylene option, have some products (e.g SPRUTT) matching the condition with the Green option in Color filter.\r\nThen, I select both of Polypropylene and 100 % polyester options, the operator for the Material filter is **'or'** and I can find the SPRUTT product in the result, but the Green option in the Color filter will disappear.\r\n\r\nCan anyone explain to me? Thanks!",
